text: Hello, i selected Snusline mostly because im from Czech Republic and Snus is kinda banned right now (as is in Europe :D ), so only "legal" shop in my country is in Prague and thats over 500km .Or i could choose this great shop with free worldwide shiping, great prices, i mean 1 snus can costs like 8€ here in Czechia while 4-5€ on Snusline, and there's just so many brands i can choose from ( mostly Skruf, that i cant buy anywhere here in Czechia ) .
